snippet.title: Crazy Chicken X | Moorhuhn X - PlayStation 2 Gameplay
snippet.description:
The PS2 version of the most popular entry in the Moorhuhn series, though it sadly lacks the mini-games included in the PSone version (which, by the way, was the last officially licensed PSone game period)

Rather than being published by Phenomedia themselves like the PSone release, the PS2 release was published by System 3 under the Play It budget label. And as often the case with Moorhuhn, it was only released in PAL regions.

Captured via PCSX2
